A state of live and death state of energy
=========================================
First of all it should be understand each and every instance of energy neither be in state of live nor in state of death, it just exits in state of streaming forever. It neither be created nor be destroyed.
Not only the existence of energy follow neither created nor destroyed principle but also the co-existence time/space/mass also follow the same principle and based on this principle everything exists in state of streaming only.

It is the purpose of simplicity/transmission of energy from one life to another life the energy can be divide in two state live and death state of energy. In fact undefined number of states energy exits. It can't be get detect by life energy since it is just a tiny state of energy.

***The purpose of transmission of energy to spark life but when it come in atmosphere get separated in two phase only, some can get spark and another get illusion too***

When energy come in state of life it can be said to be live energy since its streaming can be visualize in state of streaming in the form object, in fact object(life/body/ expression) not simply get changed but there are lot of process happen on the basis of energy internally but we can't see the all the process even a observer can look the single waves direction(its building process) of flow of energy on the basis of physical activity get proceed. Based on the power of observation/thinning of observation one can look the
thinning of the building process of energy.

***How our senses/mind look/detect the changing of physical activity/smell/sounds/touch same ways the observation state of energy can look the changing of the state of energy within
the physical activities***

Live state of energy
-------------------------------------------
Live state of energy have limitation since it have injected in some body and its first priority to keep the body live/sustain and due to that priority it create the mask of live energy, this mask of energy have much more limitation since it get realize their life have existence in the form of body/mind. In fact how much the mask of life/live energy get strong that much it get always form live energy within them. Masking is the thinking par of live energy and based on the thinking it get feel and based on the feeling it realize the feeling is right/wrong ie segregate the object/energy in the form of phases that make more rigidity/complexity of the mask of energy.

***Masking state of energy have very low intensity and stability so it can't even detect the existence of it depends up on the energy within/live energy***

Because of its limitation of its intensity, it get realization of mine/yours/relativity/gating stuck/rigidity/respect..so on. The day from when the mask of live energy get created from that day only it facing the darkness of life, confidence in life, feeling of mind/body different from the energy.

***limitation is the boundary that the limited stuff can't cross***
***limitation is not the nature of energy, it is the nature of mask energy***

Death state of energy
-------------------------------------------
Except the mask of energy/life/live, every energy are in state of death. It never recognize any object in the form of object, it have affinity towards its stability and it exists in the form of streaming. It recognize the object in the form of energy only.

Ex-
If flood/storm/earth quark come it never specially take care any saint/live/object, it is knowing all are just the state of energy and it behave same with every object as energy.
If a enlightened person put his finger in fire, fire never recognize it is the finger of enlightened person, it just recognize a finger in the form of energy.

It is the live energy who recognize good/bad, respect/un respect, living of life, happiness, pain, delight or whatever the words is used that is used by live energy, it is different
thing that the words have emotion/stability..so on. Death state of energy don't know any emotion/words, it just know the streaming/stability.

***light energy exists without any limitation, it have not any boundary like live energy***
***light energy never distinguish any live or death state of energy, it just realize every things in the form of energy only***
***light state of energy is death state of energy*** 

